**EndpointFluxMonitor**  
**Description:**  
Watches API endpoints for flux in latency, response code trends, and irregular degradation over time.

```markdown
# EndpointFluxMonitor - Latency Drift & Availability Watcher

EndpointFluxMonitor continuously scans APIs and flags shifting behavior in response quality and timing.

## Features
- Real-time endpoint monitoring  
- Drift / fluctuation detection  
- Output to CSV / JSON

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/EndpointFluxMonitor.git
cd EndpointFluxMonitor
python monitor.py
